UNITED STATES ex rel. Dominick Salvatore VICCHITTO, Relator Appellant, v. L. L. MARTINEAU, Divisional Director of Immigration, etc., Respondent-Appellee. No. 321. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. April 18, 1939. Frank A. Francis, of Hartford, Conn., for appellant.

Before L. HAND, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and PATTERSON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order, 27 F.Supp. 440, affirmed in open court. _
